{
  "number": 558,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/558",
  "title": "API proposal: starRating",
  "body": "We often want to display a list of stars instead of using the rangeSlider to refine on ratings.\n\nHere is what I've in mind:\n\n``` js\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.starRating({\n    container: '#stars',\n    facetName: 'rating',\n    max: 5,\n    labels: {\n      andUp: '& Up'\n    },\n    cssClasses: {\n      root: '',\n      header: '',\n      body: '',\n      footer: '',\n      list: '',\n      item: '',\n      active: '',\n      link: '',\n      disabledLink: '',\n      star: '',\n      emptyStar: '',\n      active: ''\n    }\n  })\n);\n```\n\n<img width=\"201\" alt=\"screen shot 2015-11-11 at 16 28 34\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/29529/11107492/485340bc-8893-11e5-93b3-9841d86d6e52.png\">\n\n``` html\n<div class=\"ais-stars-list\">\n  <div class=\"ais-stars-list--body\">\n    <div class=\"ais-stars-list--list\">\n      <div class=\"ais-stars-list--item\">\n        <div>\n          <a class=\"ais-stars-list--link\" href=\"\">\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            &amp; Up\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--count\">\n              13\n            </span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ais-stars-list--item\">\n        <div>\n          <a class=\"ais-stars-list--link\" href=\"\">\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            &amp; Up\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--count\">\n              108\n            </span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ais-stars-list--item\">\n        <div>\n          <a class=\"ais-stars-list--link ais-stars-list--link__disabled\">\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            &amp; Up\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"ais-stars-list--item\">\n        <div>\n          <a class=\"ais-stars-list--link ais-stars-list--link__disabled\">\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            <span class=\"ais-stars-list--star__empty\">\n            </span>\n            &amp; Up\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n",
